  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To identify the effects of family work shop for children with speech developmental delays.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To assess the improvement of functional performance of children with speech developmental
      delays by 2-3 hours per session, one session per week, a total of 6 weeks of family work shop
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
